wxPython Cookbook
Chapter 8 Drawing to the Screen, Using Device Contexts
Recipe 6 Reducing Flicker in Drawing Routines

This is the example code for Recipe 6 Reducing Flicker in Drawing Routines.

Prerequisites:

1) Python 2.5 or 2.6 has been installed
2) wxPython 2.8 has been installed for the version of Python used above

How to run this script:

From the command line or your IDE run the following command

python watch.py
